      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i think something is wrong. i keep having this same dream every single night lately and it's getting weird. it's like im in a pharmacy or something but there's this one specific brand of soda—blue ripple—and the logo is just glowing and everywhere. i dont even see that brand in real life but it keeps showing up in my sleep. i feel like im being targeted or something.",
