      "content": "but it's not just a dream. i noticed yesterday that right after i woke up from the most intense one, i saw a blue ripple ad in a random popup on my phone. i haven't even searched for that brand. it feels way too specific to be just \"stress.\" like, how would my brain even know what that specific logo looks like if i havent seen it? it feels like they're getting into my head somehow.",
